# Demo: Markdown + FormDown Integration

This file demonstrates that **FormDown is a true superset of Markdown**.

## Text Formatting

You can use all standard Markdown features:

- **Bold text**
- *Italic text*  
- ~~Strikethrough~~
- `Inline code`
- [Links](https://example.com)

